    "name": "Swiss-Belresort Pecatu",
    "detail": "We felt so lucky that this hotel had a room available for us to stay. It is newly built (1 year old approximately), the staff is very attentive and service minded. Especially Arvan in the reception was really nice to talk to and very helpful with scooter rental and such. Just all round a really good experience, lacking absolutely nothing. We are definetely coming back sometime and would recommend the place to anyone who wants a solid four star hotel experience to go here. PS: dont let the “five star” mark of other hotels fool you. We tried the Le Grande Bali, which claimed to be five stars, but compared to the Swiss, it was nothing. The Swiss delivers everything it promises in their four stars, and more if you ask us.",
